                Marti <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied> <expan><abbr>Tos</abbr><ex>sius</ex></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> Sur<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">a</supplied> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VIII A<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>ug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Mehrere aneinanderpassende Fragmente erhalten. Lesungs- und Ergänzungsvorschlag nach Alföldy. Z. 2 (Anfang): statt T auch E oder F möglich. Z. 2: ILJug: [d]eo s(acrum) SVR[-](?); Imamović: [d]eo s(acrum) Sur(ius); Bojanovski: [d]eo s(acrum) Sur[us?]; Škegro: [d]eo s(acrum) Sur[---]; (B): AE 1990: Z. 3: m(iles); Bojanovski: Z. 3: miles; Cubaynes: Z. 2: [-]OS SVR[---].</p>
            </div>
